
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Hello World</title>
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playfair+Display:ital,wght@0,400;0,900;1,400&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

    :root {
      --ink: #0d0d0d;
      --paper: #f5f0e8;
      --accent: #c8412b;
      --muted: #8a8278;
      --rule: #d4cfc6;
    }

    html { font-size: 16px; }

    body {
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      min-height: 100vh;
      overflow-x: hidden;
    }

    /* ── GRAIN OVERLAY ── */
    body::before {
      content: '';
      position: fixed; inset: 0;
      background-image: url("data:image/svg+xml,%3Csvg viewBox='0 0 200 200' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cfilter id='n'%3E%3CfeTurbulence type='fractalNoise' baseFrequency='0.9' numOctaves='4' stitchTiles='stitch'/%3E%3C/filter%3E%3Crect width='100%25' height='100%25' filter='url(%23n)' opacity='0.04'/%3E%3C/svg%3E");
      background-size: 180px;
      pointer-events: none;
      z-index: 100;
      opacity: .55;
    }

    /* ── HEADER RULE ── */
    .top-bar {
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 14px 48px;
      font-size: .68rem;
      letter-spacing: .18em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      animation: fadeDown .6s ease both;
    }
    .top-bar .date { color: var(--muted); }
    .top-bar .logo { font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 900; letter-spacing: .04em; }
    .top-bar nav { display: flex; gap: 28px; }
    .top-bar nav a { text-decoration: none; color: var(--ink); transition: color .2s; }
    .top-bar nav a:hover { color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .hero {
      padding: 80px 48px 64px;
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 380px;
      gap: 0 64px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    .hero-left { border-right: 1px solid var(--rule); padding-right: 64px; }

    .eyebrow {
      font-size: .68rem;
      letter-spacing: .22em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      animation: fadeUp .7s .1s ease both;
    }

    h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: clamp(3.2rem, 7vw, 6.4rem);
      font-weight: 900;
      line-height: .95;
      letter-spacing: -.02em;
      margin-bottom: 32px;
      animation: fadeUp .7s .2s ease both;
    }

    h1 em {
      font-style: italic;
      font-weight: 400;
      color: var(--accent);
    }

    .hero-body {
      font-size: .85rem;
      line-height: 1.8;
      color: #4a4540;
      max-width: 460px;
      margin-bottom: 44px;
      animation: fadeUp .7s .3s ease both;
    }

    .cta-row {
      display: flex;
      gap: 16px;
      align-items: center;
      animation: fadeUp .7s .4s ease both;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--ink);
      color: var(--paper);
      border: none;
      padding: 14px 32px;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: .72rem;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: background .2s, transform .15s;
    }
    .btn-primary:hover { background: var(--accent); transform: translateY(-1px); }

    .btn-ghost {
      background: transparent;
      color: var(--ink);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 14px 28px;
      font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace;
      font-size: .72rem;
      letter-spacing: .14em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      cursor: pointer;
      transition: border-color .2s, color .2s;
    }
    .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--ink); color: var(--accent); }

    /* ── SIDEBAR LIST ── */
    .hero-right { padding-top: 4px; animation: fadeUp .7s .35s ease both; }

    .sidebar-label {
      font-size: .62rem;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding-bottom: 12px;
      margin-bottom: 0;
    }

    .feature-list { list-style: none; }

    .feature-list li {
      padding: 18px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 28px 1fr;
      gap: 0 16px;
      align-items: start;
      cursor: default;
      transition: padding-left .2s;
    }
    .feature-list li:hover { padding-left: 6px; }

    .list-num {
      font-size: .62rem;
      color: var(--accent);
      font-weight: 400;
      padding-top: 3px;
    }

    .list-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.05rem;
      font-weight: 400;
      line-height: 1.25;
      margin-bottom: 4px;
    }

    .list-sub {
      font-size: .68rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      line-height: 1.5;
    }

    /* ── MARQUEE ── */
    .marquee-wrap {
      overflow: hidden;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule);
      padding: 18px 0;
      background: var(--ink);
    }
    .marquee-track {
      display: flex;
      white-space: nowrap;
      animation: marquee 22s linear infinite;
    }
    .marquee-item {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      font-style: italic;
      color: var(--paper);
      padding: 0 40px;
      opacity: .7;
    }
    .marquee-item::after { content: '◆'; margin-left: 40px; color: var(--accent); opacity: 1; }

    /* ── GRID SECTION ── */
    .section {
      padding: 64px 48px;
    }

    .section-header {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: baseline;
      margin-bottom: 40px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--ink);
      padding-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .section-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      font-weight: 900;
    }

    .section-link {
      font-size: .68rem;
      letter-spacing: .15em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    .section-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 1px;
      background: var(--rule);
      border: 1px solid var(--rule);
    }

    .card {
      background: var(--paper);
      padding: 28px;
      transition: background .2s;
      cursor: default;
    }
    .card:hover { background: #ede8dc; }

    .card-tag {
      font-size: .6rem;
      letter-spacing: .2em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--accent);
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }

    .card-title {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.15rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      line-height: 1.3;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    .card-body {
      font-size: .76rem;
      line-height: 1.7;
      color: #5a534c;
    }

    .card-footer {
      margin-top: 20px;
      font-size: .62rem;
      color: var(--muted);
      letter-spacing: .08em;
    }

    /* ── FOOTER ── */
    footer {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--ink);
      padding: 28px 48px;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      align-items: center;
      font-size: .65rem;
      letter-spacing: .12em;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
    @keyframes fadeUp {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(18px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes fadeDown {
      from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-10px); }
      to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
    }
    @keyframes marquee {
      from { transform: translateX(0); }
      to   { transform: translateX(-50%); }
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .hero { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .hero-left { border-right: none; padding-right: 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); padding-bottom: 40px; margin-bottom: 40px; }
      .card-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .top-bar nav { display: none; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .top-bar, .hero, .section, footer { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <!-- TOP BAR -->
  <header class="top-bar">
    <span class="date">Vol. I — Est. 2025</span>
    <span class="logo">Hello World</span>
    <nav>
      <a href="#">Work</a>
      <a href="#">About</a>
      <a href="#">Archive</a>
      <a href="#">Contact</a>
    </nav>
  </header>

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-left">
      <p class="eyebrow">Welcome — Issue No. 01</p>
      <h1>Hello,<br><em>World.</em></h1>
      <p class="hero-body">
        This is where great ideas take form. A place built on craft,
        curiosity, and the relentless pursuit of making things that matter.
        Pull up a chair — we're just getting started.
      </p>
      <div class="cta-row">
        <button class="btn-primary">Explore Now</button>
        <button class="btn-ghost">Learn More</button>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-right">
      <p class="sidebar-label">Featured</p>
      <ul class="feature-list">
        <li>
          <span class="list-num">01</span>
          <div>
            <div class="list-title">Design & Craft</div>
            <div class="list-sub">Intentional decisions at every layer</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="list-num">02</span>
          <div>
            <div class="list-title">Bold Typography</div>
            <div class="list-sub">Words that command attention</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="list-num">03</span>
          <div>
            <div class="list-title">Fluid Motion</div>
            <div class="list-sub">Animation with purpose and restraint</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="list-num">04</span>
          <div>
            <div class="list-title">Timeless Systems</div>
            <div class="list-sub">Structure built to last and scale</div>
          </div>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- MARQUEE -->
  <div class="marquee-wrap">
    <div class="marquee-track">
      <span class="marquee-item">Craft over commodity</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Form follows function</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Details define quality</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Think different</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Make it memorable</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Craft over commodity</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Form follows function</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Details define quality</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Think different</span>
      <span class="marquee-item">Make it memorable</span>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- CARDS -->
  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">Latest Work</h2>
      <a href="#" class="section-link">View all →</a>
    </div>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-tag">Identity</div>
        <div class="card-title">Brand Systems That Breathe</div>
        <p class="card-body">Logos are the tip of the iceberg. True brand identity lives in the system — color, type, motion, voice — all working as one.</p>
        <div class="card-footer">Mar 2025 · 5 min read</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-tag">Typography</div>
        <div class="card-title">Why Typefaces Change Everything</div>
        <p class="card-body">Helvetica whispers authority. Garamond exhales history. Every letter choice is a micro-decision that reshapes how readers feel.</p>
        <div class="card-footer">Feb 2025 · 4 min read</div>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <div class="card-tag">Motion</div>
        <div class="card-title">The Art of Invisible Animation</div>
        <p class="card-body">The best transitions are the ones users never consciously notice — they just feel that something is right, elegant, inevitable.</p>
        <div class="card-footer">Jan 2025 · 6 min read</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FOOTER -->
  <footer>
    <span>© 2025 Hello World</span>
    <span>All rights reserved</span>
    <span>Made with intention</span>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>